    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like there was no point to any of it. like i was just performing a role for a decade, pretending to be someone who actually knew what they were doing. now the performance is over and there's just nothing underneath. if the work was the only thing that gave my life meaning, and that's gone... what's the point in just dragging out the emptiness?",
